  ; ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  ; Sheet: CAPE-B-1 Root schematic
  ; Functional blocks:
  ;   A. PocketBeagle 2 expansion headers (P1, P2 — 2×18 2mm)
  ;   B. CAN FD — ATA6561 transceiver
  ;   C. RS-485 — MAX3485E transceiver
  ;   D. MIL-STD-1553B — DS26LV31 driver + DS26LV32 receiver + PE-68515 transformer
  ;   E. Ethernet PHY — DP83825I (RGMII0, ring node)
  ;   F. TPM 2.0 — SLB9670 (SPI0 CS2)
  ;   G. SiK 915MHz MAVLink radio (UART3, RFD900x module)
  ;   H. LoRa — RFM95W 915MHz (SPI)
  ;   I. WiFi/BT — TI WL1837MOD (SDIO + UART BT)
  ;   J. RCRS-49MHz RC receiver header
  ;   K. ATF16V8BQL CPLD write-blocker (microSD log protection)
  ;   L. W25Q128JV NOR Flash (SPI circular log)
  ;   M. microSD card socket (CPLD-guarded)
  ;   N. DRV8833 dual H-bridge (payload bay actuators)
  ;   O. HX711 load cell ADC
  ;   P. Power input + debug UART
  ; ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

  ; ── Global power symbols ─────────────────────────────────────────
